g.style: fill:#000000; fill-opacity:1;stroke:#000000; stroke-opacity:1; stroke-linecap:round; stroke-linejoin:round;

g.text: SDA/SCL_RPi is the bus between the STM, the RPi, and the ATTiny.
It is exposed at J12, which is DNP.
The Pull-Up resistors are on the RPi.
SDA/SCL_INT is the internal bus, which goes between the STM and the charger IC.
It is exposed at J11, which is populated to allow access to other I2C devices.
The Pull-Up resistors are on this board, and have values of 1.8k.
